TY  - JOUR
T1  - Contact and Group Structure: A Natural Experiment of Interracial College Roommate Groups
AU  - Chakravarti, Arjun
AU  - Menon, Tanya
AU  - Winship, Christopher
Y1  - 2014/04/28
PY  - 2014
DA  - 2014/08/01
